    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Monstrous men described in the Florentine Codex as the fifth omen that heralded the arrival of the Spaniards to the Mexica. Literally, "man (as) poisonous (or thorny) plants".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
